i throughout the hotel, mini-bar, tea and coffee-makers, coffee and espresso machine and in-room safe. Our Signature rooms and above include access to our Signature Lounge including buffet breakfast, non-alcoholic drinks throughout the day and evening canapes served with Happy Hour cocktails.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4803vhnv buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"\/rooms-suites\/\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-xs    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">READ MORE<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4803to4q fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\"><\/span><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-4803to4u fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy.jpg 900w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c7db6dfa2c771466ad022516ae8093db_Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c7db6dfa2c771466ad022516ae8093db_Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy-768-c-100.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-4803to4v fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">INTERESTING FACTS<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-4803to50 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>Caravelle Hotel opened on Christmas Eve, 1959, and was the city&rsquo;s premier venue for grand balls and functions. Since then it has welcomed countless dignitaries, politicians and celebrities.<\/p>\n<p>In 1975, it was renamed Doc Lap (Independence) Hotel, commemorating Vietnam&rsquo;s liberation. The original hotel was closed in the mid-1990s for refurbishment, with the addition of the new 24-storey tower, and re-opened on 8 May, 1998.<\/p>\n<p>Saigon Saigon Bar, voted the &lsquo;Best Bar&rsquo; in the city and Top 10 Exciting Entertainment Venues, dates back to 1959 and retains the original charm of original 10-storey hotel&rsquo;s rooftop bar. It was once a famous gathering place for war correspondents.<\/p>\n<p>In 2001, Caravelle Hotel hosted the cast and crew filming Graham Greene&rsquo;s epic novel The Quiet American, starring Sir Michael Caine.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.ffb-id-4803s70d{ \npadding-top: 50px;\npadding-right: 50px;\npadding-bottom: 50px;\npadding-left: 50px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70i ,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:after,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70i{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:after,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:focus,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:after,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:focus{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70i{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70i ,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:after,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i:focus,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:after,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803s70i *:focus{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70h ,\n.ffb-id-4803s70h:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70h:after,\n.ffb-id-4803s70h *,\n.ffb-id-4803s70h *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803s70h *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803s70h{ \nfont-