 center\">We exceed 5 star expectations by providing sincere, professional service and comfort.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Our sense of leadership, autonomy and individuality allows us to be flexible and capable of adaptation to the needs of every single &ldquo;guest&rdquo;.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Our mantra: We leave you smiling.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-480426si fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\"><\/span><\/span><h2 class=\"ffb-id-480426sn fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">VISION<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-480426so fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle is to be the iconic hotel in Ho Chi Minh City.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">We continue to build on our history, location, reputation and our sincere service standards to create a one-of-a-kind hospitality experience, whether our guest is from Vietnam or from overseas.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">We continually refine our best practices and our individual skill-sets through training.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">We&rsquo;ll lead by example, draw from a continually deepening knowledge base and exercise all of our skills to deliver warm, luxury service.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Past, present and future guests make us their FIRST CHOICE when visiting Ho Chi Minh City.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-480435sf fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-480435sh fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">VALUES<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-480435si fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">GUEST FIRST - Exceed 5 Star Expectations, Deliver Luxury Service, Continual Improvement.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">WARMTH - Friendliness, Yes We Care, Professional, Heart of Saigon.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">RESPECT - Agility, Autonomy, Adaptability, Flexibility for Our Guests&rsquo; Changing Needs.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">HARMONY - Teamwork leaves guests smiling, we are First Choice for Past, Present, Future Guests.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">INTEGRITY - Reputation, Genuine, Comfortable, Protect like Family Member.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">KAIZEN - Continuous Improvement, Change is Good, Change one person at a time, Positive Change, Change before you have to.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.ffb-id-4803to4i{ \npadding-bottom: 50px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to4q{ \npadding-top: 0px;\npadding-right: 30px;\npadding-bottom: 30px;\npadding-left: 30px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to50{ \npadding-right: 30px;\npadding-left: 30px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to50 ,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:before,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:after,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:after{ \ncolor: #797979 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to50{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to50:before,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:after,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:focus,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:after,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:focus{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to50{ \nfont-size: 16px !important;\nline-height: 24px !important;\nfont-weight: normal !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-4803to50 ,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:before,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:after,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803to50:focus,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:before,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:after,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-4803to50 *:focus{ \nfont-size: 16px !important;\nline-height: 24px !important;\nfont-weight: normal !important;\n}\n@media (min-width:768px) 